	<a href="images/biopics/Jim.jpg" data-lightbox="Bios" data-title="Jim is an archaeologist and historian with a particular interest in the Native peoples of the Northeast. He has worked in historic preservation, been a museum director, coached lots of students, and is now self-employed, which means writing articles and books. He has a deep commitment to social justice, music in almost any form, and good science fiction. With Peggy, his best friend, wife and editor, he loves to garden, tend bees, canoe or what ever else she cooks up.">
